<TextField id="select" label="Age" value="20" select>
  <MenuItem value="10">Ten</MenuItem>
  <MenuItem value="20">Twenty</MenuItem>
</TextField>
`}
            </FuseHighlight>
            <Typography className="mb-16" component="div">For a <a href="#native-select">native select</a>, you should mention a label by giving the value of the <code>{`id`}</code> attribute of the
